      "id": "MAIN_CHAMBER",
      "name": "The Mechanist's Laboratory",
      "description": "A vast, circular hall with polished gray stone floors. Bright magical orbs float near the ceiling, casting a cold, even light. The room is organized into distinct zones: an armory table to the north, a shelf of glowing liquids to the east, two training dummies in the center, and a pile of massive boulders to the west."
    }
  ],
